Data pulled from a MCU of a salvaged Model 3. VIN is encoded in the HRL files.

## HRL Format

The HRL file format seems to consist of blocks of length 0x4000 bytes. It appears each block starts with two bytes 0x4000 which seems t
o denote the size of the current block.
Bytes 2 and 4 seems to be an incrementing number.

Here are the block begins:
